name: Something in the Way
wikiSummary: The last track on the breakthrough album "Nevermind", the song was featured in the Sam Mendes' 2005 film, "Jarhead".  The rumor that "Something In The Way" is about Kurt Cobain living under a bridge as a teenager is false. Kurt did live under a bridge, but this is not what "Something In The Way" is about.
wikiText:
The last track on the breakthrough album "Nevermind", the song was featured in the Sam Mendes' 2005 film, "Jarhead".
 
 The rumor that "Something In The Way" is about Kurt Cobain living under a bridge as a teenager is false. Kurt did live under a bridge, but this is not what "Something In The Way" is about.
